OL,6,FA man from Sussex has spoken of his
OL,7,Fbattle to overcome a life-changing
OL,8,Fbrain injury he suffered when he "was
OL,9,Fleft for dead" in a hit and run in
OL,10,FOctober 2022.
OL,12,FMads Vallestad, 30, was walking home
OL,13,Fafter returning from a holiday to
OL,14,FItaly when he was struck by a blue
OL,15,FFord Fiesta which had mounted the
OL,16,Fpavement in Rusper Road, Horsham.
OL,18,FThe driver fled the scene. Mads was
OL,19,Ffound unconscious on the pavement
OL,20,Falong with a rucksack he was carrying.
