OL,6,FHis suitcase, which had been dragged
OL,7,Fby the car, was found 200 metres away.
OL,9,FMads suffered a traumatic brain injury
OL,10,Fand fractured skull. He spent six
OL,11,Fweeks in hospital, including around
OL,12,Ftwo weeks in an induced coma in
OL,13,Fintensive care.
OL,15,FThe electronics engineer had to have
OL,16,Fpart of his skull removed.
