OL,3,CHit and run victim determined to
OL,4,Covercome life-changing brain injury
OL,6,FHe is now using Action for Brain
OL,7,FInjury Week to speak of his
OL,8,Fdetermination to overcome his injuries
OL,9,Fthe best he can and warn of the
OL,10,Fconsequences of dangerous driving.
OL,12,FMads, who also suffered multiple
OL,13,Ffacial fractures, a broken right
OL,14,Fcollarbone and right big toe, said:
OL,15,F"Although I feel lucky to be alive
OL,16,Fevery aspect of my life changed that
OL,17,Fnight.
