OL,3,CHit and run victim determined to
OL,4,Covercome life-changing brain injury
OL,6,F"I was left for dead and I feel it's
OL,7,Fonly because of the actions of those
OL,8,Fwho came to my aid and the emergency
OL,9,Fservices and doctors that I survived."
OL,11,FFollowing the incident, which happened
OL,12,Fat around 9.30pm on 16 October, 2022,
OL,13,FMads' parents, Terje and Berit who
OL,14,Fwere in Australia, flew back home to
OL,15,Fbe by their son's bedside.
OL,17,FHe remained in an induced coma until 6
OL,18,FNovember and was was discharged from
OL,19,Fhospital on 27 November, 2022.
