OL,6,FBefore the collision Mads, had been
OL,7,Fsaving to buy a house, but has had to
OL,8,Fdelay this because his injuries. He is
OL,9,Fstill unable to work full-time and is
OL,10,Fon a phased return.
OL,12,FMads said: "I spent six weeks in
OL,13,Fhospital but that was just the start
OL,14,Fof it. Once home I continued to suffer
OL,15,Fwith problems and went from being an
OL,16,Findependent and outgoing person to one
OL,17,Freliant on my family.
