OL,6,F"I had to give up a lot of my hobbies
OL,7,Funtil I had the titanium plate fitted
OL,8,Fand lost interest in going out and
OL,9,Fmeeting my friends. I've had to delay
OL,10,Fbuying a house due to the injuries and
OL,11,Fthe need to work on my recovery.
OL,13,F"The trauma my brain suffered still
OL,14,Faffects me now. While I'm making
OL,15,Fprogress in my recovery I still
OL,16,Fstruggle with reading, my speech and
OL,17,Fremembering things.
