OL,4,Covercome life-changing brain injury
OL,6,F"I'll always be upset and angry at
OL,7,Fwhat happened and how the driver left
OL,8,Fthe scene. However, I want to focus on
OL,9,Fmy recovery and my future. I know I
OL,10,Fstill face many challenges, but I'm
OL,11,Fdetermined to do everything I can to
OL,12,Freclaim more of my old life. The
OL,13,Fsupport I've had from my friends and
OL,14,Ffamily but also my rehab team has been
OL,15,Famazing. I couldn't have made the
OL,16,Fprogress I have without them.
