OL,6,F"I just hope that by speaking out
OL,7,Fpeople who may be in a similar
OL,8,Fsituation don't feel they have to go
OL,9,Fthrough it alone. Help and support is
OL,10,Favailable."
OL,12,FFollowing the collision, Sussex police
OL,13,Ffound fragments of the Fiesta at the
OL,14,Fscene. They recovered CCTV which
OL,15,Fshowed the vehicle travelling on the
OL,16,Fwrong side of the road prior to the
OL,17,Fcollision. The driver was traced.
